#To-do List#
📎 Link
Project Demo Link: to-do-list-edyg.vercel.app

📋 To-Do List App with Calendar Integration
Welcome to the To-Do List App! This project is a simple yet powerful tool for managing your tasks and schedule. With a built-in calendar, it helps you organize your day, week, and month effectively.

🚀 Features
Task Management: Create, edit, and delete tasks.
Calendar Integration: View tasks and deadlines on a calendar interface.
Dynamic Styling: User-friendly interface built with HTML and CSS.
Real-Time Updates: Responsive task list powered by Node.js and JavaScript.

🛠️ Technologies
This project is built using:
Node.js: Backend development and API handling.
JavaScript: Client-side logic and interactivity.
HTML & CSS: Structuring and styling the user interface.


